<L>__{interior command center}
<A>__{the officers are directing the placement of every moveable item in front of the oil drums. desks, crates, chairs, food, all are heaped in front of the fuel. all the workers cast frequent nervous glances back at the burning cartridge boxes across the court. suddenly the worst begins to happen at the cartridge boxes. hundreds of thousands of live cartridges begin exploding, flying around the court like shrapnel. hot lead begins to zing off the exposed fuel drums, leaving big dents.}
